{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5435c86e1f","title":"在印度大使举行的印度国庆会上的祝词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a6c8ff0ad8","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":26,"articleId":"5435c86e1f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"9366f01c2e","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"5435c86e1f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"月26日是印度的国庆日。这是毛泽东在印度大使举行的印度国庆会上的祝词。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8335cb884e","type":"title","text":"在印度大使举行的印度国庆会上的祝词”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"5435c86e1f"},{"id":"9366f01c2e","type":"paragraph","text":"印度民族是伟大的民族，印度人民是很好的人民。中国、印度这两个民族和两国人民之间的友谊，几千年以来是很好的。今天庆祝印度的国庆节日，我们希望中国和印度两个民族继续团结起来，为和平而努力。全世界人民都需要和平，只有少数人要战争。印度、中国、苏联及其他一切爱好和平的国家和人民团结起来，为远东和平、为全世界的和平而努力。庆祝印度国庆，祝贺印度人民，祝贺你们的总统。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"5435c86e1f"}],"page":{"id":"ea84cea5b2","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"5435c86e1f","start":76,"end":76}}}},"__N_SSG":true}